    <div><p>The <a href="https://www.gamerating.org.tw/Search/" target="_blank">Taiwan Digital Game Rating Committee</a> has rated the unannounced <em><a title="Games > Devil May Cry 5 Devil Hunter Edition" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/devil-may-cry-5-devil-hunter-edition">Devil May Cry 5 Devil Hunter Edition</a></em> for <a title="Platforms > Switch 2 [1,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch-2">Switch 2</a>. <span id="more-1036545"></span></p><p><em><a title="Games > Devil May Cry 5 [42 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/devil-may-cry-5">Devil May Cry 5</a></em> first launched for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/601150/Devil_May_Cry_5/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on March 8, 2019, followed by <em><a title="Games > Devil May Cry 5 Special Edition [10 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/devil-may-cry-5-special-edition">Devil May Cry 5 Special Edition</a></em> for Xbox Series on November 10, 2020, and PlayStation 5 on November 12, 2020.</p><p>Here is a screenshot the rating:</p><figure><a data-featherlight="image" href="https://www.gematsu.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/DMC5-Switch-2-Rating_03-26-26_Rating.jpg"></a></figure><p>Thanks, <a href="https://nintendoeverything.com/devil-may-cry-5-seemingly-coming-to-nintendo-switch-2-getting-new-devil-hunter-edition/" target="_blank">Nintendo Everything</a>.</p></div>

        
    
